{"tid":106721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱咪咪感謝觀眾冇離棄 ：其實大同細又有咩分別喎","createTime":"2017-02-04T01:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T18:50:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"591f10412e2493f6219b7fdda73542ac8bfcad8c","tid":106721,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"[俾人睇唔起] 朱咪咪感謝觀眾冇離棄 ：最大嘅歌星咪又係開4面台<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170203/56258876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170203%2F56258876&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=df8bbcc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170203%2F56258876&h=5264818a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170203/56258876</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486130427_53e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486130427_53e1.jpg&h=73b2f5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱咪咪一連兩場嘅《利利是是演唱會 2017》今晚喺紅館舉行，演唱會喺8點30開騷，話晒咪咪姐有一定嘅號召力，全場爆滿一啲唔難，唔少仲係上咗年紀觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/39/Youknoweat.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F39%2FYouknoweat.gif&h=e81d77e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪咪姐著住鑲滿銀色珠片嘅灰色裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一出場先唱咗首《白金升降機》後同觀眾拜年：「恭喜發財！祝大家新一年更美好、更順利、更健康，今日係人日，每人都生日，全世界生日。」佢唱咗一段生日歌後再講：「祝大家身體健康，日日有工開、餐餐有飯食、日日有好運、晚晚有覺瞓。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129885_3f9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129885_3f9a.jpg&h=a83930ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住台上出現咗4隻貼滿LED燈嘅舞獅上台，咪咪換另一套紅色長裙上台，佢話：「我好少著紅色衫，因為人哋話我著紅色衫好淫蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過新年冇計，我過年好傳統，一見獅子就要摸吓獅頭俾封利是，咁就全年好運。」咪咪姐帶住一隻獅圍住台邊行，觀眾好熱情咁爭住摸獅頭兼俾利是，咪咪好搞笑話：「摸獅頭唔好摸第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔好獅子都非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」結果逗利是逗到手軟，多到差啲拎唔晒，佢仲話：「我奶奶嗰封一定要攞，唔係叫個仔休咗我點算！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129889_21dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129889_21dc.jpg&h=69fd6aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逗完利是之後，咪咪姐話：「今次係我最後一次開演唱會，之前好多記者朋友問我係咪有病，我話：『啋！你就有病！』只係做一次個唱好多嘢要準備，我想下半生舒服啲啫！以前人哋話不離不棄嘅係夫妻，𠵱家不離不棄嘅係手機，我手機係打出打入，whatsapp我都係幾個月前先識用，電子嘢我無興趣，不離不棄嘅係你哋！」<br />\n<br />\n咪咪姐仲有感而發話：「好多人知我冇經理人又冇簽大公司，最大間嘅係TVB，我知道好多同行睇唔起我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢啲唔係大公司製作，唔緊要，我只係想開開心心，同大家好似自己人咁傾吓計唱吓歌，其實大同細有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最大嘅歌星咪又係開4面台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔通可以開6面咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？所以同大家開開心心咁唱歌最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」"},{"pid":"258f5cf224d4ecb6e6769e0900350209f96e60ce","tid":106721,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129880_5a3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129880_5a3b.jpg&h=a4dedfab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咪咪姐話最後一次喺紅館開騷，因為好多嘢要籌備，只係想下半生舒服啲啫！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129883_eee1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129883_eee1.jpg&h=b2a002e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咪咪姐感謝觀眾不離不棄！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129887_82bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129887_82bf.jpg&h=a179f270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咪咪姐話摸過獅頭，成年行好運！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486129894_1034.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486129894_1034.jpg&h=8c2e30fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢逗利是逗到手軟！"},{"pid":"b96eb5d6dd9067b13a83462c201ec263300338f7","tid":106721,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:50:00.000Z","msg":"佢有咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}